                    "body": "```suggestion\r\nlemma vecMul_self_mul_conjTranspose_eq_zero_iff (A : Matrix m n R) (v : m → R) :\r\n    vecMul v (A * Aᴴ) = 0 ↔ vecMul v A = 0 := by\r\n  simpa only [conjTranspose_conjTranspose] using vecMul_conjTranspose_mul_self_eq_zero_iff Aᴴ _\r\n```",
